lyrics:
[Verse]
In enchanted woods, where the fairies dwell
There lies a shop, where all dreams excel
All the Fae Things, a haven so rare
Where mystical wonders, they freely share

[Chorus]
Come join the dance, in radiant light
All the Fae Things, enchanting sight
Guided by whispers, through realm and wing
Embrace the magic, let your heart sing
